    },
    {
      "id": "SPD-008",
      "quote": "Harrington advises that it is much easier to go from a fast swing speed and improve accuracy while maintaining swing speed. He warns that it is almost impossible when you try to pick up swing speed later on.",
      "bucket": "LEARNING_AND_IMPROVEMENT",
      "physical_tag": "speed_training",
