      "physical_tag": "speed_training",
      "emotional_tags": ["key_differentiator", "technical_insight"],
      "source": "https://brucebolt.us/blogs/news/how-to-increase-golf-swing-speed",
      "speed_mentioned": null,
      "priority": "HIGH"
    },
    {
      "id": "SPD-013",
      "quote": "I would rather see a player with 20-year-old clubs and a monitor on the range than a player with brand new clubs and no monitor.",
      "bucket": "EQUIPMENT_AND_TECHNOLOGY",
