      "emotional_tags": ["inconsistency", "tempo_issues", "power_loss"],
      "source": "https://hackmotion.com/how-to-increase-clubhead-speed/",
      "speed_mentioned": null,
      "priority": "HIGH"
    },
    {
      "id": "SPD-022",
      "quote": "A faster swing speed means more distance, which can significantly reduce your strokes on longer holes.",
