      "speed_mentioned": null,
      "priority": "STANDARD"
    },
    {
      "id": "SPD-024",
      "quote": "But it's not just about power; it's also about control. A well-executed fast swing maintains accuracy while maximizing distance, giving you an edge on the course.",
