    },
    {
      "id": "SPD-030",
      "quote": "A typical session might include 8 swings with a lightweight setting, followed immediately by 8 swings with a heavier configuration. This contrast helps your body recruit fast-twitch muscle fibers more effectively, leading to increased clubhead speed with your actual driver.",
