      "speed_mentioned": null,
      "priority": "STANDARD"
    },
    {
      "id": "SPD-044",
      "quote": "If your body is stiff, your swing will always be limited, no matter how strong you are. Mobility exercises help you rotate further and faster, store more energy, and release it into the ball.",
